OL,7,FThieves have targeted 'life-saving
OL,8,Fequipment' from a fire station that
OL,9,Fcost thousands of pounds to replace.
OL,11,FA fire engine was left unusable after
OL,12,FNewport Fire Station was targeted by
OL,13,Fthieves on Monday (19 Feb), because
OL,14,Fthe theft of a thermal imaging camera
OL,15,Ftook out the engine's wiring.
