OL,7,FThe fire engine is now back an action,
OL,8,Fwith the thermal camera replaced
OL,9,Fquickly due to how vital the equipment
OL,10,Fis for daily emergencies, but those
OL,11,Fwho work at the station say the theft
OL,12,Fis an insult to the community they
OL,13,Fserve.
OL,15,FA door to the fire station was also
OL,16,Fdamaged as the thieves gained entry to
OL,17,Fthe building during the early hours of
OL,18,Fthe morning.
