OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,FThe station's Watch Manager, Charlie
OL,8,FCartwright, said the theft could have
OL,9,Fput lives at risk.
OL,11,F"I'm very disappointed to believe that
OL,12,Fsomeone could take life saving
OL,13,Fequipment from the community, and
OL,14,Fpotentially equipment that could save
OL,15,Fthem as well."
OL,17,FCraig Jackson, from the fire service
OL,18,Fsaid: "We're talking around #5,000
OL,19,Fworth of equipment that was taken,
OL,20,Fit's equipment that our crews utilise
OL,21,Fto rescue people from house fires.
