OL,5,Cstation
OL,7,F"We just ask that the community
OL,8,Fremains vigilant, and looks out for
OL,9,Fthe fire station, because it's their
OL,10,Fcommunity fire station.
OL,12,F"So please report anything suspicious
OL,13,Fto the police."
OL,15,Fsaid the incident is being
OL,16,Finvestigated, and thanked local
OL,17,Fbusinesses and neighbours for helping
OL,18,Fwith their enquiries.
