OL,7,FDetective Constable Julia Hiller said:
OL,8,F"We're taking it very seriously, it's
OL,9,Fan important facility for Newport.
OL,11,F"The community has been brilliant,
OL,12,Flocal businesses have supplied CCTV,
OL,13,Fand we've gone from house to house,
OL,14,Fthey've been fantastic."
